flowchart TD
    A[main.py\nCLI entry] --> B[Load customer profile\nInitialize AgentState]
    B --> C[Append user message\nRun LangGraph]
    C --> D[supervisor_node]
    D --> E{Route decision}

    E -->|Home Loan| H1[home_loan_specialist]
    E -->|Gold Loan| G1[gold_loan_specialist]
    E -->|Credit Card| K1[credit_card_specialist]
    E -->|Transactions| T1[transaction_specialist]
    E -->|Offers| O1[offers_specialist]
    E -->|Loan Calc| L1[loan_product_calculator]
    E -->|Banking| B1[banking_specialist]
    E -->|Ambiguous| Q1[Ask clarification]

    H1 --> S[synthesis_node]
    G1 --> S
    K1 --> S
    T1 --> S
    O1 --> S
    L1 --> S
    B1 --> S
    Q1 --> S

    S --> F[main.py cleanup\nshort terminal response]
    F --> C

    H1 -. uses .-> HC[customer offer scope\nhome loan only]
    G1 -. uses .-> GC[customer offer scope\nplus live gold price]
    K1 -. uses .-> KC[customer offer scope\ncredit card offers]
    T1 -. uses .-> TC[transactions]
    O1 -. uses .-> OC[offer catalog + scores]
    B1 -. uses .-> BC[customer profile + memory]

